Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要誇自己幹得不錯了  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,總之要先安頓好朱音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,頭撞到哪裡了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正细雅宋_GBK\fs45\bord0.5\blur7\3c&HACB0B6&\fade(0,100)\frz359.9\pos(308,603)}去
